  <p>Northdale's family appeal and proximity to top-rated schools keep quality homes in demand. Updated single-family homes near the golf course and community parks tend to lease quickly and hold strong rents. Condos and villas offer dependable returns for investors seeking lower-maintenance assets.</p>
